let info = {

    {
      id: 1,
      title: "Acme Proposal Meeting",
      invitees: "dave, john, bob, carol",
      matching_terms: ["dave", "john", "bob", "carol", "acme"],
      date: "2019-01-10 10:00:00",
      type: "calendar",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      title: "Acme Final Delivery Meeting",
      invitees: "dave, john, bob, alice",
      matching_terms: ["dave", "john", "bob", "alice", "acme"],
      date: "2019-03-01 11:00:00",
      type: "calendar",
    },
  ],
  contacts: [
    {
      id: 1,
      name: "John Doe",
      company: "Acme Inc",
      emails: ["john@acme.co", "doe@gmail.com"],
      phones: ["650-555-5555", "+44 171 5555 5555"],
      matching_terms: ["acme", "john", "john doe"],
      last_contact: "2019-02-26",
      type: "contacts",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      name: "Robert Roe",
      company: "Acme Inc",
      emails: ["bob@acme.co"],
      phones: ["+44 171 6666 5555"],
      matching_terms: ["acme", "robert", "roe", "bob"],
      last_contact: "2019-02-29",
      type: "contacts",
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      name: "Alice Smith",
      company: "Other Corp",
      emails: ["alice@other.co"],
      phones: ["+1 415 555 6666"],
      matching_terms: ["alice", "other", "alice smith"],
      last_contact: "2019-02-29",
      type: "contacts",
    },
  ],
  dropbox: [
    {
      id: 1,
      path: "/taxes/2016/w2-acme.pdf",
      title: '"2016 W2"',
      shared_with: ["jane@accountants.com", "spouse@family.org"],
      matching_terms: ["tax", "w2", "alice"],
      created: "2016-02-01",
      type: "dropbox",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      path: "/work/customers/acme/invoice.docx",
      title: '"ACME Corp: Invoice"',
      shared_with: ["acme-accounts@mycompany.com"],
      matching_terms: ["acme", "invoice"],
      created: "2019-02-01",
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      path: "/purchases/2016/fridge.pdf",
      title: '"Best Buy: Invoice"',
      matching_terms: ["invoice"],
      created: "2019-02-01",
      type: "dropbox",
    },
    {
      id: 4,
      path: "/work/customers/acme/proposal.docx",
      title: '"ACME Corp: Draft MoU"',
      shared_with: ["acme-accounts@mycompany.com"],
      matching_terms: ["acme", "proposal", "mou"],
      created: "2019-01-19",
      type: "dropbox",
    },
    {
      id: 5,
      path: "/work/customers/acme/meeting-notes.docx",
      title: '"ACME Corp: Meeting Notes"',
      shared_with: ["acme-accounts@mycompany.com"],
      matching_terms: ["acme", "meeting notes"],
      created: "2019-02-04",
      type: "dropbox",
    },
  ],
  slack: [
    {
      id: 1,
      channel: "chatter",
      author: "alice",
      message: "Who's up for lunch right now?",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 11:00:00",
      matching_terms: ["alice", "chatter", "lunch"],
      type: "slack",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      channel: "chatter",
      author: "bob",
      message: "I am up for lunch!",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 11:00:01",
      matching_terms: ["bob", "chatter", "lunch"],
      type: "slack",
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      channel: "chatter",
      author: "carol",
      message: "Me too @alice!",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 11:00:02",
      matching_terms: ["carol", "chatter", "alice"],
      type: "slack",
    },
    {
      id: 4,
      channel: "customer-chatter",
      author: "alice",
      message: "Did any of you meet with Acme folks last week?",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 12:00:00",
      matching_terms: ["alice", "customer-chatter", "acme"],
      type: "slack",
    },
    {
      id: 5,
      channel: "customer-chatter",
      author: "dave",
      message: "Yeah, I met with Bob there",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 12:00:01",
      matching_terms: ["dave", "customer-chatter", "bob"],
      type: "slack",
    },
    {
      id: 6,
      channel: "customer-chatter",
      author: "dave",
      message: "I think John from Acme was in that meeting too",
      timestamp: "2019-02-26 12:00:02",
      matching_terms: ["dave", "john", "acme"],
      type: "slack",
    },
  ],
  tweet: [
    {
      id: 1,
      user: "@acmecorp",
      message: "We're hiring in Boston!",
      timestamp: "2019-02-29",
      matching_terms: ["acme", "hiring", "boston"],
      type: "tweet",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      user: "@acmecorp",
      message: "We're no longer hiring in Timbuktu",
      timestamp: "2019-02-27",
      matching_terms: ["acme", "hiring", "timbuktu"],
      type: "tweet",
    },
  ],
};

export default info;
